name: NBM2019_ParadeOfHomesAd
description:
pg horizontal  7.75 x 4.875 |
This magazine is distributed to all who attend the parade of homes and all builders. This is an excellent way to be recognized as a construction lender. NBC also has a home that they financed on the parade and could benefit from showcasing that property. This ad targets builders, new construction borrowers, realtors who sell land and then refer the construction financing. An ad in this magazine will help draw attention to the fact that NBC is a player in construction loan arena. They have an excellent product and quick turn around time. Targeting this group of people will lead to increased mortgage volume and market share. Includes project management, creative direction, writing, trafficking, and design.
